data.description: Attention Investors and Veterans!! VA loans accepted!! This home feats 4beds and 3 full baths, porcelain flooring in 1st and 2nd floor baths, stainless steel kitchen appliances, microwave, new side door, large patio, washer & dryer stays. Roof is approx. 7 yrs old. New hot water heater is scheduled to be installed asap. Location is just a short drive to the new FCC Soccer stadium, Downtown Cincinnati, Bengals and Reds stadiums. Check it out!!
